Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Software Engineer position with FedEx Freight. I bring over three years of professional experience in full-stack software development, AI/Machine Learning, and cloud-native systems, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

