I have always been passionate about customer focus, innovation, and delivering high-value technology solutions and envision myself contributing my talent to the furthering of FedEx Freight's mission to provide superior financial returns through high-value logistics, transportation, and information services. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

